## Scope of this license

This MIT license applies to the contents of the Paperclip Startup Template package:

- All Markdown documents (`AGENTS.md`, `HEARTBEAT.md`, `SOUL.md`, `TOOLS.md`, `COMPANY.md`, `README.md`, the `docs/` directory, this `LICENSE`).
- The `.paperclip.yaml` manifest.
- Any scaffolding, examples, or reference material shipped in the package root.

Companies instantiated from this template are independent works owned by their respective operators. The MIT terms above govern the template package itself, not the products built on top of it.

